Wenger on Alexis' Arsenal future: &quot;I have spoken through text and it was very positive. My thoughts are always positive.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger on whether he's convinced Alexis Sanchez will stay: &quot;Of course. There is not a lot to resolve at the moment with the player.&quot;

Mourinho, &quot;I think the Arsenal board have given Wenger the treatment he deserves.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mourinho, &quot;After Chelsea, United were the most successful club last season and then it was Arsenal.&quot;
